overview: From filmmaker Richard Corso (The Salesman, Picnic Under A Gibbet) and based on the story, ‘You Little Etcetera, You’ by Gregory Ferbrache, The Switcheroo Room is a mystery-drama film set in the dark underbelly of the Golden Age of Hollywood where a group of actresses, DeEtta Jain, Ryan Lucy, Emma Moody, Haleigh Burckley and Aletheia Matthews, await casting in the roll of the lifetime.
title: The Switcheroo Room
